{"tid":1344604,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[超合作運動］發起全民帶鐵通出街活動","createTime":"2019-07-21T23:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T01:08:47.000Z","uid":80234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a6fe5f002c9e55d1d8fabfd550209533e826289f","tid":1344604,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:52:45.000Z","msg":"尋日元朗警黑勾結事件，警方眾目睽睽下目睹黑社會人仕帶鐵通/棍都話見唔到人持有武器，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJd7FkD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJd7FkD.png&h=f3bf70b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見有白衫拎棍就當打棍球身份證都唔查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCEyAUi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCEyAUi.png&h=c7eb7207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑衫係南邊圍對開經過就嚴陣以待，一字排開扣查<br />\n<br />\n警方嘅選擇性執法已經顯示政府同警方已經毫無正當性，合法性合理性，官商鄉黑勾結昭然若揭<br />\n<br />\n聽過有種和理非行動以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幽默宣示對抗暴政嘅決心</span></strong></span>，當然其他更實際行動有待大家商討及支持<br />\n<br />\n好似烏克蘭當年禁戴頭盔出街，當地民眾紛紛配戴各類頭盔出街以示對該法例不滿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgyvDdP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgyvDdP.png&h=f14ac891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當香港非法管治者宣布持鐵通/棍攻擊普通市民後都冇後果，作為和理非嘅市民，我呼籲大家響應政權，起碼每日拎枝<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">田徑棒</span></strong></span>出街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4WAPiu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4WAPiu.png&h=5ae4ba39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>薪火相傳，全民運動，對抗暴政</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bab5708f2084b4dcff79813808d2ff6588a7787d","tid":1344604,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:04:31.000Z","msg":"ｐｕｓｈ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1e774641cef6508f7f0d10ce031f32be2d1e19","tid":1344604,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:08:47.000Z","msg":"支持<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民頭盔鐵通 </span></span>"}]}